      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-17/spacex-s-nasa-monopoly-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[滞留的NASA宇航员，Butch Wilmore和Suni Williams明天将在SpaceX的Dragon胶囊上重返地球。彭博社的布鲁斯·埃因霍恩（Bruce Einhorn）谈到了SpaceX如何开发了将NASA宇航员穿上太空的垄断。他与Caroline Hyde和Tim Stenovec进行了交谈。]]></description>
